#	Configuration file for the Shu-Osher problem
#	Ref: Shu, C.-W. and Osher, S., J Comp Phys 83:32-78 (1989)

REQUIRES Driver
REQUIRES physics/Hydro
REQUIRES physics/Eos


D  sim_rhoLeft		Density in left part of grid
D  sim_rhoRight		Density in right part of grid
D  sim_pLeft		Pressure in left part of grid
D  sim_pRight		Pressure in right part of grid
D  sim_uLeft		Fluid velocity in right part of grid
D  sim_uRight		Fluid velocity in right part of grid
D  sim_aRho             Amplitude of the density perturbation
D  sim_fRho             Frequency of the density perturbation
D  sim_posn	        Point of intersection between the shock plane and the x-axis
D  sim_nsubint          Number of subintervals to average over to get cell-averages.
 
PARAMETER sim_rhoLeft	REAL    3.857143
PARAMETER sim_rhoRight	REAL    1.0
PARAMETER sim_pLeft	REAL    10.33333
PARAMETER sim_pRight	REAL    1.0
PARAMETER sim_uLeft	REAL    2.629369
PARAMETER sim_uRight	REAL    0.
PARAMETER sim_aRho	REAL	0.2	
PARAMETER sim_fRho	REAL	5.0	
PARAMETER sim_posn	REAL	-4.0
PARAMETER sim_nsubint	INTEGER	100